  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下基础设施层的流量走向。核心是PM这个负载均衡器，它要向下游分发到几个关键组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，PM作为中心节点。那上游有哪些服务会调用PM？我看到有TECH和NFWB？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "TECH",
        "NFWB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，TECH是技术服务的负载均衡入口，NFWB是Redis缓存层，它们都指向PM。注意NFWB到PM是反向依赖，PM要回读缓存数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TECH",
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把NFWB和TECH作为上游画出来，用左向箭头表示它们指向PM。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "TECH",
        "PM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "然后PM向下游分发，需要连三个组件：RES也是Redis缓存做响应加速，EMG是Ingress控制器处理路由，NYSDEC是另一个负载均衡做区域分流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "RES和NFWB都是Redis缓存，但角色不同对吧？NFWB是上游数据源，RES是PM下游的写入缓存？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RES",
        "NFWB",
        "PM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，NFWB是Infra_RedisCache实例但属于数据层上游，RES是PM主动写入的结果缓存。方向别搞反了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "RES",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "清楚了，PM到RES、EMG、NYSDEC都用右向箭头，表示PM主动发起的下游调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说的NFWB方向可能让你误解了。NFWB到PM虽然是数据回流，但图上要体现PM依赖NFWB，所以是NFWB指向PM的左箭头，不是PM指向NFWB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，我确认一下：NFWB[Infra_RedisCache] <-- PM，TECH <-- PM，然后PM -- RES，PM -- EMG，PM -- NYSDEC。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "TECH",
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，TECH也是Infra_LoadBalancer类型，和PM、NYSDEC同类，但它是独立的上游入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TECH",
        "PM",
        "NYSDEC",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我调整好了。整个流向从左到右：TECH和NFWB作为上游输入，PM做中心调度，然后分发到RES、EMG、NYSDEC三个下游。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TECH",
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个拓扑清晰了。PM作为核心负载均衡，既承接上游流量，又分发到缓存、路由器和区域负载均衡，符合我们架构设计的意图。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
